Package: easyML
Type: Package
Title: Easy Machine Learning Pipeline for Supervised, Unsupervised, Causal, and Reinforcement Learning
Version: 2.4.0
Date: 2026-03-22
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jose", "Ventura-Leon",
           email = "jventuraleon@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2996-4244"))
    )
Description: Simplifies machine learning workflows for classification,
    regression, and unsupervised learning tasks. Provides single function
    interfaces: supervised_ml() for supervised learning and unsupervised_ml() for
    clustering, dimensionality reduction, and anomaly detection. Supervised
    pipeline handles preprocessing, model training, hyperparameter tuning,
    evaluation, and interpretability. Unsupervised pipeline automates k-means,
    hierarchical, DBSCAN, GMM clustering with optimal k selection (silhouette,
    elbow, gap statistic), PCA/t-SNE/UMAP reduction, and anomaly detection
    (Isolation Forest, LOF, Mahalanobis). Includes sample size estimation
    tools (ml_sample_size) and advanced splitting methods. Built on tidymodels.
